{"tid":1606301,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［夢遊］模擬普選","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T14:57:17.000Z","uid":249040,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a77e8f158a712279bd4b3cbd70a6e824e11016","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:59:05.000Z","msg":"其實可能黎唔切 但諗左好耐 點樣可以對準普選呢個最終訴求 顯示出最多人民力量又唔洗送頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發夢夢到 同一日各區自己搞模擬普選<br />\n<br />\n只需要各區設置眾多 QR code，比人嘟手機投票，目的係所有人落街實踐呢個模擬普選， 以最終投票人數，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">向世界顯示香港大多數人普選的決心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n有埋d類似票站裝飾最好， 比人清左一個點無所謂，就去當區其他點。 好似連儂牆咁，流動性大， 風險少。<br />\n<br />\n最大好處係 好多中立甚至淺藍都好想普選嘅，呢種形式門檻又低， 最終肯出黎嘅人數一定可以多好多！ <br />\n<br />\n試想像下， 向全世界表態 你唔比我普選， 我都動員到全城人一齊出黎模擬普選個種道德力量， 國際輿論一定 like！ <br />\n<br />\n利申： 仲係夢遊幻象中"},{"pid":"839bcb9e69fc9cf963ce4eb4b50203144f7d881f","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:00:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9aff3e516209f2a4cdea4ae62b62a1569568ed9d","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:02:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2329a57ef1fae5f20e352925813bf53acf3c378f","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51adfcadbe9bfc0a208cab2cdf0d34f5e3a586b5","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:04:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e271a21aac5ccedc37c7a4a37344164107f61af7","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:05:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8200f327f38200ebc25f4fadd8b777b1328d1656","tid":1606301,"uid":249040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aeef05dc8daf7850d466454a9d21dfd61f44d5d7","tid":1606301,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"Telegr